data.description: Welcome Home to 251 Bailey Ave in the Heart of Rock Hill! This charming brick home features 3 bedrooms with primary down, spacious living area and family room with fireplace, open concept kitchen with breakfast area. Spacious laundry room with plenty of storage in this home. Sunroom overlooking back deck and private pool, perfect for year round entertaining. Second floor has spacious guest rooms and a shared bathroom and even more storage space. The private backyard is filled with wildlife, perfect for bird watching and relaxing by the pool. This home has amazing curb appeal, prime location and mature landscaping all around. No HOA. Located minutes from shopping, restaurants, hospital and I-77.
